<slide>
	<title>Installing Xdebug</title>
	<subtitle>Compiling</subtitle>

	<blurb>With PEAR:</blurb>
	<list class="numbered">
		<bullet>pecl install xdebug-2.1.0RC1</bullet>
		<bullet>*Ignore:* %You should add "extension=xdebug.so" to php.ini%</bullet>
	</list>
<break/>
	<blurb>Without PEAR:</blurb>
	<list class="numbered">
		<bullet>wget http://xdebug.org/files/xdebug-2.1.0RC1.tgz</bullet>
		<bullet>tar -xvzf xdebug-2.1.0RC1.tgz</bullet>
		<bullet>cd xdebug-2.1.0RC1</bullet>
		<bullet>phpize</bullet>
		<bullet>./configure</bullet>
		<bullet>make</bullet>
		<bullet>make install</bullet>
	</list>
<break/>

	<blurb>Tailored installation instructions: <link href="http://xdebug.org/find-binary.php"/></blurb>
</slide>

